<Description>
    <Header>
        <h5><b>Alignment</b></h5>
    </Header>
    <Content>
        The legend alignment property controls how legend items are aligned
        within the legend container. This example demonstrates aligning the
        legend items to the far end by setting the <code>Alignment</code> property to <code>Alignment.Far</code> in the <code>ChartLegendSettings</code> component for improved visual balance.
    </Content>
</Description>

