<Description>
    <Header>
        <h5><b>Reverse (Inversed)</b></h5>
    </Header>
    <Content>
        The inversed property allows you to reverse the order of legend items.
        This is useful when the series rendering order needs to be displayed
        in reverse within the legend for better comparison. This can be achieved by setting the <code>Reverse</code> property to <code>true</code> in the <code>ChartLegendSettings</code> component.
    </Content>
</Description>

