<Description>
    <Header>
        <h5><b>Toggle Visibility</b></h5>
    </Header>
    <Content>
        The <code>ToggleVisibility</code> property allows users to show or hide a series by clicking on
        its corresponding legend item. This example demonstrates how this feature can be used to compare
        different product categories' revenue more effectively.
    </Content>
</Description>

